## 8. Common Pitfalls to Avoid

### 1. Using MutableState directly in ViewModel

```kotlin
// âŒ Bad
class MyViewModel : ViewModel() {
    val state = mutableStateOf(UiState())
}

// âœ… Good
class MyViewModel : ViewModel() {
    private val _state = MutableStateFlow(UiState())
    val state = _state.asStateFlow()
